Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rage on! Rage on! Rage on! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Moeagare! Moeagare! Moeagare GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must run forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,If you are still burning with furious rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mada ikari ni moeru toshi ga aru nara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of space cities\Nhad been built around the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and people lived their lives\Nin this second home to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking to impose its dictatorship\Nover all of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...it waged a war\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After evading a Zeon attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base escaped from\Nthe space city Side 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and landed on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla's Agony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Still unable to contact Federation HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base heads west\Nacross Central Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The young crew is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All they can do is carry out\Ntheir assigned duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should sleep more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you are a pilot, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confirmed by astronomical observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here at the appointed place,\Nat the appointed time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet there's no word from General Revil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We left the communication circuit open...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't send it by radio anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...considering we're in\NZeon territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, someone's going to walk here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To the middle of this desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all tired at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla, make sure everyone continues\Nto monitor for aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for your hard work.\N- No, thank you all. Here's some breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this around to everyone.\NWe're all on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for not noticing, but\Nwe're almost out of salt. Can we get more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt? You mean, salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something moving at 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like an off-road cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please confirm on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum magnification.\N28 kilometers ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the port-side machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will be landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Steady now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do butterflies fly in the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Butterflies in the desert...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the thorns of a cactus\Nfly in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sent by General Revil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll take over as driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunmalo gave him some\Nemergency first aid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Bright Noa,\Nresponsible for the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Odessa Day is scheduled\Nfor 5 days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ordered to bring the White Base\Nacross the Caspian Sea by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Odessa Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when we'll start an offensive against the\Nmain forces of M'Quve, Kycilia's subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The mines held by M'Quve\Nare considered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...a strategic asset that will determine\Nthe outcome of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack them on Odessa Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the White Base\Nwill take part in the offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not part of the military.\NRight, Mr. Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's suffered too much blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the White Base is being incorporated\Ninto the regular forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- It's about that salt shortage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you noticed until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a direct hit on the stores\Nin the fighting the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our salt supplies were destroyed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Zeon's strongest forces\Nare ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's doubtful we can get salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The lack of salt will affect\Ncombat performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, aren't you finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be done for some time.\NHow could I be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still warm, so eat soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get in touch with General Revil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now they're saying we have no salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat, Amuro! Eat, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt? You mean the kind you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou'll die if you don't get enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Promise you'll eat.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Aren't you finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There! A saline lake,\Nalong the old Silk Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- A saline lake?\N- Yes. It's a lake that contains salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go there, we may get some salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator. Can we head toward the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we don't run into M'Quve...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...we won't have any problem with any route.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just assume there'll be less resistance\Nif we go around the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so unlike you, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If our information is correct,\Nwe should see the Trojan Horse soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We should also contact Lord M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lady Kycilia's jurisdiction after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Open a line to Captain M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain M'Quve Is not here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He Instructed me to provide you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Ensign Uragang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well-prepared as always.\NI will contact you when I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My regards to the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Hamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly is well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that one must be cautious\Naround Lord M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a guerrilla soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be headed back to space\Nonce I avenge Lord Garma's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we spread\Nour net around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A charming sound, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Is it a precious item?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Northern Sung Dynasty.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've informed Ramba Ral\Nas per your instructions, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Captain M'Quve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have new information from intelligence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ship thought to be the Trojan Horse{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're moving away from my mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uragang, inform Ramba Ral of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner he gets rid of the Trojan Horse,\Nthe less he'll be hanging around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\Nwe don't want Admiral Dozle to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...the truth about the mines I discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve's underlings are quite dutiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...telling us the Trojan Horse\Nhas taken a detour to avoid us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I don't know.\NWhat do you think Lord M'Quve is up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry too much, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! The lake's gone!\N- Disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure looks like there\Nwas a lake here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the map! Is there no mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, there is no error.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I ran out of salt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've made White Base wander off-course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeons must have seen us by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker. Is there any other data on this lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lob Lake... a salt lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Moves east to west like a pendulum\Nevery 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- How old is the map in our data?\N- Must be from before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There haven't been any map-making\Nsatellites since the war began.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's move. We'll pursue that lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Direction is 2 o'clock.\NOne vehicle, on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the type is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you identify it from the speed,\Naltitude, or mass?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one enemy vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too fast to be a Magella Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Too small for a Gaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, can you head out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to fight without knowing the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this is a job for Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm launching the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, level 1 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam, Guncannon,\Nand Guntank on stand-by!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll launch when we know a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're at level 1 battle stations.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Ramba Ral, Acous,\Nand Cozun in the field yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Gallop will make a broadside attack\Non the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Ral and the two Zakus\Nwill destroy it, like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's in the Gundam, Mr. Job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! She said she had special orders!\NAre you saying she doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there aren't any special orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, please get out of the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Catapult engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I figured this out\Nthrough the simulations, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the G force would be this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Port-side, return fire!\NPrepare beam cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guncannon, Guntank!\NCover the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin evasive maneuvers,\Nbut don't stop firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll go into action any moment now.\NUntil then, keep the enemy engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I have to make contact\Nwith a Zeon soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A Zaku from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming properly, but... no hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought targeting would be so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot seems to be inexperienced.\NSorry, but I'm taking you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vulcans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Get up! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If necessary, I'll transfer to the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably has the radio off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit for long-range support, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks tough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't confirmed the hit yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's the pilot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit isn't such an easy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If the sand hadn't acted as a cushion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...even this Gouf mobile suit\Nwould have been finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not giving me a chance to aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get him into grappling range!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cozun! Don't be a fool! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, Lieutenant Ral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll capture this mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The auto-balancer doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Ral, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll plunder this mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The main camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The cameras are being crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, could you cut one of its\Npower pipes with your heat rod?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take this one back to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that new mobile suit\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there's no way we can save It!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But just keeping up with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...is taking everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've split up the Zakus too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Cozun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to immobilize it on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous! Can't you get past the red one\Nand over to Cozun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Open the radio circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just use brute force!\NStrength isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I'm out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous! Acous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozun, get back! Acous has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acous?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Acous been... killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Get away from there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Ral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozun! Cozun! Answer me! Cozun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,l-ls he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamon! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring in the Gallop! Let's rendezvous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Clamp, were you able to detect the Gouf?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll contact it in 50 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Acous and Cozun were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- But... that's so frustrating, Ms. Hamon.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have that new Zanzibar warship.\NWhy couldn't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we deploy something\Nthat's still being tested?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, Admiral Dozle\Nthinks that Ramba Ral...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...has enough fighting strength to defeat\Nthe Trojan Horse and the mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... I feel frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Lord M'Quve's cooperation,\Nwe'll face some tough battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you treat prisoners\Naccording to the Antarctic Treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you won't be fed well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're barely keeping ourselves fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups don't give a second thought\Nto us guys on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. The warrior woman returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Sayla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Sayla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll see you on the bridge later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to prove that a woman\Ncan fight as well as a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was that your only reason?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, someone as clever as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we must set an example\Nfor the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days solitary confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Meal for the prisoner?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you are not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what's happened to Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Char? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Char Aznable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his position\Nafter he failed to protect Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How much it would cost to buy me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only three days, so please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me, Mr. Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call for me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother...\NChar is my big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure of It.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad he's all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There! A lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! Who would've thought\Nit would move so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can get our salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozun, the prisoner, attempts to escape\Nwith the Federation's top secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, the unrelenting power\Nof the Gouf's heat rod...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...burns away at the Guncannon's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Amuro rescue Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro Deserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro Deserts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:54.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:59.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:09.63,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:14.55,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:19.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:24.56,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:29.15,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:39.45,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:54.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:59.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:09.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:14.55,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:19.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:24.56,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:29.15,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:39.45,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
